column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name], p.objID, specphotoall.specobjid, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as type, SpecPhotoall.petrotheta_u FROM #x x, #upload u, PhotoTag p LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll ON p.objID = SpecPhotoAll.objID WHERE u.up_id = x.up_id and x.objID = p.objID and p.type = # and specphotoall.specobjid IS NOT # ORDER BY x.up_id
